Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all, Guiche?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My speciality is earth magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been doing nothing but playing knight from dawn to dusk and calling it training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're enjoying themselves, so what's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like someone wants to object.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand your feelings with Saito busy with the Order every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't have any problem with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I admit that we haven't had much time to talk despite his coming back from the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:00:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffocating me, Tiffa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you decided to come to the academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you told me to muster the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a secret that I'm a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I promised that I'd protect you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big smile on his face all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going\Nwithout saying a word to your master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where else other than the Order's training?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as yesterday and the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I'm off to training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so mad about so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to spend more time together like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get it, you dense dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I-I want you to come home earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you need me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like more tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your afternoon schedule looking like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please schedule some time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa became popular in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hottest topic on campus right now is whether her great breasts are real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery must be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's come down to this, I shall find out with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmo will kill you, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening to anything I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I was, Reinard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saying we should recruit more\Npeople into the Order of Undine Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but how do we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's another chevalier on this campus other than Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hat will suit your beauty the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this hat will look the best on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? It's got to be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, if they take her hat off, they'll find out she's a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine. Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what a rude girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insolent wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees me like this, I bet he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a master's duty to give presents once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I will welcome Saito back kindly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for leaving you unattended!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You notice that now? But just one apology isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for getting caught up with playing knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for staring at Tiffania's breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then, demonstrate your thoughts with action!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, I always wanted to hold you tight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever leave you alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a chevalier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So would you join the Order of Undine Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Gallian citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in playing knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice Yvonne von Guldenhorf-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guldenhorf-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Beatrice of the Grand Duchy of Guldenhorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to be in the same class with the Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet you don't even come to introduce yourself to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Utter insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her your apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. I'm sorry, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that an apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that dirty hat off first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're before an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a limit to how rude you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this hat is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tell you to take it off, you take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing to Tiffania?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know who she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No matter who she is, she shouldn't bully others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't Princess Guldenhorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello, Mr. Gramont.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy here is Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barbarian that was just appointed a chevalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you talk with a man like this in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll ruin your eminence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he came and{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mature lady shouldn't show any weakness at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's fine, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the next time you are to take that dirty hat off in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Guiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be from a really honourable family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you deferring so much to an underclassman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a bad person to be on the bad side of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's just a small independent\Nnation, she is a princess of a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really rich and has her personal guards here with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're called the Luft Panzer Ritter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're known as the strongest dragon knights in Halcheginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to get in trouble with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have deployed an entire Knight\Ndetachment for their daughter at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wealthy like to put on a display.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about their dragon knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they ever come to you for anything, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, Louise. Give him the best smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Saito! Hurry, come and sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I already ate with Guiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to discuss something with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I wanted to ask you about this too, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Tiffania's being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're related to a duke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would talk to{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you very kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should just leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A word of warning won't{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it's her own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She chose to come here of her own will, so she should take care of herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what was on your mind all these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order training? Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Order's got nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed now, so don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said to come back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, suit yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him? I've been waiting for hours,\Nand he gets carried away when I'm being nice to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he cares about is that half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière, you'll be late for your classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't get a wink of sleep, so I'm not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll skip school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cause any more trouble for Saito-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Westwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Westwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she absent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Westwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What strange clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This robe is a memento of my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Only nomads wear such robes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you by any chance an e-e{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an elf, and she became more popular than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down! I want to be friends with you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lie! There's no way an elf won't do anything bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elves have certainly been the enemies of\Nhumans in Halcheginia for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my parents fell in love with each other and gave me both elf and human blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're a half-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask. What god do you worship?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The desert's devil? Or the Primogenitor, Brimir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to be friends with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you believe in the same god as we do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then prove that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guldenhorf Grand Duchy, Luft Panzer Ritter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a little noisy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Saito... Stupid Saito... Stupid Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An inquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to be a bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prove your faith to me, a deputy of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's just the right temperature for\Nanyone who believes in the Primogenitor, Brimir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't anyone stopping this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of the dragon knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is an inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you side with her, they'll treat you as a heretic and send you to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, go back to where you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll treat it as though none of this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have always wanted to see the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san and everyone else made that dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell you to go home, then you'll go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pity you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I guess that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunk her in the pot! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare interrupt the inquiry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So leave Tiffa{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. This isn't only about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will cause an inquiry to befall your beloved, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beloved?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who brought Tiffa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with all this begging?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're a heretic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about, Mr. Gramont?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame on knighthood to forsake ladies and one's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knights are to decide things with wands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help acting cool when there's such an audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undine, draw your wands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Luft Panzer Ritter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you wake me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are being noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having such a good dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so close, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You interrupted the inquiry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had better beware of the consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inquiry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you mean the bishop's license, I have it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To perform an inquiry, you need the Romalia Sectarian Head's written permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bishop should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't have the right? She uttered God's name in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've got nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know elves were so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to be her friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the cruel treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally fell in a state of panic. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I think I can make lots of good friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'd like to say everything's solved,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's one thing I must definitely ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise isn't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r} Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your familiar is interesting as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're here to be cynical?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is difficult to get down on one's knees in that situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you interrupt an inquiry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your beloved will be questioned as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He bowed his head after hearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who he thought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do these look that fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's talking about them,\Nand even the Principal asked a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a reason why everyone is\Nwondering, but I can't tell what that might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa... What are you suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...touch and check?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only person I can ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you want me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea why they don't look real?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not yet. I think I need to inspect them a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one to see him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my familiar, so I should be first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have a whip on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Luckily, I happen to have one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Louise! Don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm furious right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you want to shame yourself even more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Captivating Girl's Bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a hole, you want to hide in it, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
